channel.title: Venom
channel.description:
Welcome to Venom
I basically hosted this server for awhile, wasn't feeling it to much, so i quit it. I've done alot of stuff to it. Fixed some bugs, edited everything i could, it isnt much, but its alot different then the regular delta **** out there. Credits: 95%Delta 5%Me
Server Features: *Mole Lair- Added Giant Mole lair, added some cool drops, plus correct emotes for him.
*Ice Lair- Basically moved the island from delta here, added hellhounds, ice giants, and an ice queen. Ice queen is a boss, drops good loot, and hellhounds and giants drop good loot as well.
*Lava Lair- Same as ice lair, only added it in a cool cave, added fire giants who hit hard with decent loot, and mage hitting black demons for boss.
*Meat Tenderiser- Added meat tenderiser with correct attack emotes, also added a cool spec to it.
*New Barrows- Nothing major, just added the barrows from the minutes tut, only with (what i tried) to make a similar barrows tunnels like RS
*Barbarian Assault- Changed npc's and location of assualt minigame, also added drags instead of warriors, added correct emotes for drags, as well as changed rewards for the game
*Barrage and Blitz freeze- where its basically impossible to move.
*Added a cool free for all PvP game, where it can be any level vs any level and you dont lose items.
*Spread out shops all over varrock
*Added more and moved metal drags to a multi zone at about lvl 30 wild.
*Changed up PC rewards.
*Made basically the entire economy based on monster drops.
*Some more stuff that I can't remember.
*Client.Java is about 555kb, and i had about 1100 character files as well.
Pics: Black Demon [img]http://i36.tinypic.com/15oidk7.jpg[/img] Home [img]http://i35.tinypic.com/v66oud.jpg[/img] Ice Lair [img]http://i38.tinypic.com/23js3r6.jpg[/img] Lava Lair [img]http://i35.tinypic.com/x1bp6d.jpg[/img] Barbarian Kills [img]http://i37.tinypic.com/ih78uw.jpg[/img] Barbarian Rewards [img]http://i37.tinypic.com/2j7eo3.jpg[/img] Barrows Tombs [img]http://i35.tinypic.com/2yzlzpi.jpg[/img]] Free For All Area [img]http://i35.tinypic.com/2rwqgw8.jpg[/img] Meat Tenderiser Spec [img]http://i36.tinypic.com/25r09rc.jpg[/img] Mithril Dragons [img]http://i36.tinypic.com/a5i144.jpg[/img] Giant Mole [img]http://i33.tinypic.com/wqo7td.jpg[/img] Pest Control Rewards [img]http://i38.tinypic.com/6xxftw.jpg[/img]
